                <div type="section" xml:id="WORKSBYOTHERS">
                    <head type="section">Works by Others</head>
                    <p>If, in the encoding of the early manuscripts, we discover an intervention by a writer other than <persName corresp="#JR">Ruskin</persName>
                        or if we find that <persName corresp="#JR">Ruskin</persName> transcribed without substantially altering a text by another writer, we
                        encode and class these texts as <hi rend="italic">works by others</hi>. Just as for works by <persName corresp="#JR">Ruskin</persName>, links default to an Apparatus
                        Page.</p>
